SUNSET MOUNTAIN ROAD...... that name was EARNED and not just given!!!!  You must come visit this incredible 33 acre ranch and SEE FOR YOURSELF!  BREATHTAKING VIEWS FOR MILES & MILES !!!!!  Super Secluded at the very end of the road !!! NO TRAFFIC AND LITTLE TO NO NOISE!!!
EXCELLENT COMBINATION of cleared pasture land with sandy loam for livestock and hardwood cover for abundant wildlife.  Super Sturdy house with tons of windows, UPGRADES, and character!  SANTO ISD!!!
